item.title: Christmas List
item.description: Here’s my Christmas list: One of these mice: Glorious Model O Matte Black [$49.99] (link) Xtrfy M42 RGB Black or Miami Blue (pre-order only, should be out early December) [$59.00 for Black or $65.00 for Miami Blue] (link) Some RAM for my PC (Patriot Memory Viper 3000Mhz 8GB Dual Channel DDR4) [$35.99] (here’s a link) Anker SoundBuds Curve Upgraded 2019 (it’s the best budget wireless earbuds according to rtings.
